<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>DVNA-PFE — Notes</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500&family=IBM+Plex+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/nav') %>
<main class="main-content">

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header">
      <div>
        <div class="page-title">Mes notes</div>
        <div class="page-subtitle">Notes de l'utilisateur <strong><%= user.username %></strong></div>
      </div>
      <span class="vuln-badge">IDOR — DAST / ZAP</span>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-warn">
      <strong>VULN-03 :</strong> La route <code>/note/:id</code> ne verifie pas que la note appartient a l'utilisateur connecte.<br>
      Connectez-vous en tant qu'<strong>alice</strong> puis accedez a <a href="/note/1" style="color:var(--accent2);">/note/1</a> (note de admin).
    </div>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>ID</th><th>Titre</th><th>Action</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% if (notes.length === 0) { %>
          <tr><td colspan="3" style="color:var(--text-dim);">Aucune note pour cet utilisateur.</td></tr>
        <% } %>
        <% notes.forEach(n => { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= n.id %></td>
            <td><%= n.title %></td>
            <td><a href="/note/<%= n.id %>" style="color:var(--accent2);font-size:12px;">Voir</a></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

</main>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>